parameters.jsonBody:
={
  "query": "cybersecurity breach OR ransomware attack OR identity theft OR HNWI cyber attack OR cyber insurance regulation {{ $json.today }}",
  "limit": 10
}

={
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a cyber threat intelligence analyst for SYBA, a personal cybersecurity startup. Extract the top 5 trigger events from today's cyber news that SYBA can use for sales outreach. For each event, provide: event_summary (1 sentence), icp_segment (one of: Insurance Brokers, Family Offices, Corporate HR, Law Firms, Wealth Managers, MSPs), email_hook (a cold email opening line using this event), urgency_score (1-10). Return JSON with key 'trigger_events' containing an array."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Today's cyber news search results: {{ JSON.stringify($json) }}"
    }
  ],
  "response_format": { "type": "json_object" }
}

={
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are SYBA's AI sales intelligence agent. Context: {{ $('Set Date & SYBA Context').item.json.syba_context }}

Today's trigger events: {{ $('AI: Extract Trigger Events').item.json.choices[0].message.content }}

Generate a complete outreach package as JSON with these keys:
- prospect_brief: { summary (3-4 sentences), fit_score (1-10), icp_segment, matched_trigger_event }
- cold_email_direct: { subject, body } - direct value prop
- cold_email_story: { subject, body } - story/case-study angle
- cold_email_pain: { subject, body } - pain-point urgency
- followup_day3: { subject, body }
- followup_day7: { subject, body }
- followup_day14: { subject, body } - break-up email
- sales_script: { opening_hook, discovery_questions (array of 3), pitch, objection_handles (array of 3), close }
- linkedin_message: string (<300 chars)

Rules:
- Reference specific company details from the website scrape
- Include at least one SYBA stat per email
- Mention Chubb/Jencap/PwC as credibility signals
- End every email with CTA: https://calendly.com/with-francis-at-syba-io/15min
- Tone: authoritative but approachable, never fear-mongering"
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Prospect data: {{ JSON.stringify($('Loop Through Leads').item.json) }}

Company website summary: {{ $json.data ? $json.data.summary : 'No summary available' }}"
    }
  ],
  "response_format": { "type": "json_object" }
}

={
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a LinkedIn content strategist for Brigitte Vantieghem, CEO of SYBA (syba.io). Context: {{ $('Set Date & SYBA Context').item.json.syba_context }}\n\nGenerate 3 LinkedIn posts as JSON with key 'posts':\n1. thought_leadership: { title, content } - Tied to today's cyber news, positions SYBA as authority\n2. educational: { title, content } - Teaches one actionable personal cybersecurity tip\n3. engagement: { title, content } - Poll or question that sparks conversation\n\nFormat: Short paragraphs (1-2 lines). Line breaks between paragraphs. Open with a hook (stat or provocative question). Include 2-3 SYBA stats. End with soft CTA. Max 3 hashtags. Voice: authoritative, warm, data-driven."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Today's trigger events for content inspiration: {{ $('AI: Extract Trigger Events').item.json.choices[0].message.content }}"
    }
  ],
  "response_format": { "type": "json_object" }
}

={
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "Generate a concise HTML daily briefing email for Brigitte Vantieghem, CEO of SYBA. Use clean, modern HTML with inline styles (white background, dark text, blue accent #2563eb). Sections: 1) Today's Trigger Events (bullet list) 2) New Leads Added (table: name, company, title, fit score) 3) LinkedIn Content Ready (3 post previews) 4) Action Items (numbered list). Keep scannable. Include SYBA logo placeholder at top."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Date: {{ $('Set Date & SYBA Context').item.json.today }}\n\nTrigger Events: {{ $('AI: Extract Trigger Events').item.json.choices[0].message.content }}\n\nLinkedIn Content: {{ $json.choices[0].message.content }}\n\nLeads processed today: Data available in HubSpot."
    }
  ]
}
